{"tid":219634,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"青政被DQ正是反骨禍港報應，泛民逆天而行被拉也是活該","createTime":"2017-04-27T10:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T17:36:45.000Z","uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4727f37614632ea5eb94c229c3593321dc0a8e3","tid":219634,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:47:04.000Z","msg":"青政被DQ，本民青見財化水，<br />\n正是反骨禍港報應，泛民逆天而行被拉也是活該。<br />\n<br />\n我早跟你地講左青年新政累街坊，你地總係唔聽，當晚死要走出去吸光環。<br />\n<br />\n當晚有幫青年新政既撚樣都係天生犯賤，<br />\n其實睇番佢地做過乜野都知道，青年新政從不為人民抗爭，但係就要人民為佢抗爭。根本就離撚晒譜。<br />\n<br />\n今日俾人拉鳩晒都係抵撚死既。你地冇一個值得可憐。<br />\n這是你們地應該承受的報應。["},{"pid":"b8e6d4a3be1b07557e2af12fe81ba04200d80e93","tid":219634,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:48:56.000Z","msg":"鳩硬呢隻垃圾"},{"pid":"d553a4a7421fa6a5640b564a11b3fa880344b871","tid":219634,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鳩硬呢隻垃圾</blockquote><br />\n講真話俾人話垃圾。<br />\n笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b889dcf287bede47fd821f1cbee9eba1e166d174","tid":219634,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0825e6408d575567cf9ca1a981cfb4284980c2c","tid":219634,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"熱狗全面收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da3ece287894c220bf1bd7081e4a49bd1708477","tid":219634,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鳩硬呢隻垃圾</blockquote><br />\n講真話俾人話垃圾。<br />\n笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾鳩軟無撚用做乜出嚟獻世啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"h